1. *Lijevo* od mene je moj brat. (My brother is *left* of me.)
2. Kada vozim, uvek držim ruke na *lijevoj* strani volana. (When I'm driving, I always keep my hands on the *left* side of the steering wheel.)
3. Da biste došli do prodavnice, skrenite *lijevo* na raskrsnici. (To get to the store, turn *left* at the intersection.)
4. Neki ljudi preferiraju da pišu *lijevom* rukom umesto desne. (Some people prefer to write with their *left* hand instead of their right.)
5. *Lijeva* strana moje glave boli kada imam glavobolju. (The *left* side of my head hurts when I have a headache.)
6. Ovaj ormar ima tri *lijeva* krila. (This wardrobe has three *left* wings.)
7. Stavio sam svoju jaknu na *lijevu* policu. (I put my jacket on the *left* shelf.)
8. *Lijevo* oko mi je zasuzilo zbog jakog vetra. (My *left* eye watered because of the strong wind.)
9. Nisam siguran šta se nalazi *lijevo* od ove zgrade. (I'm not sure what's *to the left* of this building.)
10. Dok sam trčao, osetio sam bol u *lijevoj* nozi. (While I was running, I felt pain in my *left* leg.)